About US


OUR COMPANY
Greme Limited is a real estate firm that provides facilities management,agency and consultancy services for residential and commercial properties. The full scope of our services encompasses feasibility and market analysis,letting and selling as well as property advisory services. With more than seven years in the industry, Greme has a multidiscplinary professional team committed to applying innovative and proven strategies to create sound solutions to every day real estate challenges. We offer outstanding customer service and care to provide complete and tailored property management services to our clients. our staff are equipped with the appropriate tools, have the expertise and experience to deliver efficient services. At Greme Investment, we value our Landlords and respect our tenants.
OUR MISSION
To set the standard for the best proffesional property management in Kenya.
Our Vision
