Maximum Occupancy

Become fully digital with automated tenant onboarding. Get the best tenants faster and have agreements & handover protocols signed with exactly 3 clicks! Digital signing, first invoices, deposit management, and welcome emails are automated.
Invoices Sent

With Bidrento, all your invoices are automatically sent out, tracked, and sent to your accounting. Invoices for rent, utilities, and extra services. Advanced cost allocation, rent indexation, temporary price changes, and discounts are done with ease.
Money Received

Get paid faster and on time from tenants. All payments are matched with the right invoices and synced with your accounting. Deposits and prepayments are handled, penalties are calculated, and debt management is done. Reminders are sent out automatically.
Happy Tenants

The Bidrento Tenant app ensures a great experience for your tenants, providing answers and access to everything they need while occupying your spaces. They can pay their bills, order additional services, submit maintenance requests, and know their consumption and CO2 footprint.
Single Source of Truth

Discover the convenience of a unified database. Bidrento consolidates essential documents - invoices, agreements, meter readings - in one secure location. Say goodbye to misplaced files and incomplete documentation. All data is up to date, and reports are always available.


Building Maintenance

Building maintenance is completed on time, and all documentation is stored and available anytime. Bidrento will automatically create a future maintenance plan, and after the service provider completes their task, all documentation and feedback will be stored.


Happy Team

Bidrento is an easy-to-use system with extensive automation. All team members and departments stay up to date with modern, flexible tools. They call it AI - we call it Bidrento.

